<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Couple Shower Games</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/Couple_shower_games.css">
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="shower-hero-game">
    <div class="overlay">
      <h1>Couple Shower Games</h1>
      <p>Celebrate love with laughter, games, and unforgettable moments.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro Section -->
  <section class="shower-intro-game">
    <p>
      Planning a couples’ shower? These interactive games are perfect for bringing everyone together — whether you're hosting at home, in a garden, or at a venue. Break the ice, spark laughter, and make the bride and groom-to-be feel special.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Game Grid -->
  <section class="shower-games">

    <div class="shower-card">
      <img src="/img/488ec4ffb09a3552e731c7f3ad114978.jpg" alt="He Said, She Said">
      <h3>He Said, She Said</h3>
      <p>Guests guess who said what between the couple. Prepare for lots of laughs and a few surprises!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="shower-card">
      <img src="/img/ec86c93d7fc13280730b8aa18e2a1bc8.jpg" alt="The Newlywed Game">
      <h3>The Newlywed Game</h3>
      <p>Ask each person questions about their partner and compare answers. A fun test of how well they really know each other!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="shower-card">
      <img src="/img/9cc2a8055d91b24cc60a4d941c8c6195.jpg" alt="Couple Bingo">
      <h3>Couple Shower Bingo</h3>
      <p>A sweet twist on Bingo using couple facts, shared hobbies, and their love story. Great for getting guests involved!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="shower-card">
      <img src="/img/a284e0269074baeb242a4530ded5c5cc.jpg" alt="Who Knows Best">
      <h3>Who Knows Them Best?</h3>
      <p>Guests compete to see who knows the couple’s favorites, firsts, and funny quirks the best.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="shower-card">
      <img src="/img/f8c65fb9adf0fa657905f4b06646362c.jpg" alt="Date Night Jar">
      <h3>Date Night Jar</h3>
      <p>Each guest writes a unique date night idea. The couple draws one for a future night out!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="shower-card">
      <img src="/img/87d9e393ae2d4830446f1c6c69d45725.jpg" alt="Photo Memory Match">
      <h3>Photo Memory Match</h3>
      <p>Match childhood photos, travel memories, and funny moments to the right partner — a lighthearted and memorable icebreaker everyone will enjoy.</p>
    </div>

  </section>

</body>
</html>
